spec_data.Name: texlive-latexfileversion
spec_data.Description:
This simple shell script prints the version and date of a LaTeX
class or style file. Syntax: latexfileversion <file> This
programme handles style files (extension .sty), class files
(extension .cls), and other TeX input files. The file extension
must be given.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 06 Aug 2017 08:18:03 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Prints the version and date of a LaTeX class or style file
